  <lyrics>
	<stanza type="verse" number="1">Teach us to pray that we may cause
  The enemy to flee,
That we his evil pow'r may bind,
  His prisoners to free.</stanza>
	<stanza type="verse" number="2">Teach us to pray and firmly stand
  Upon the battleground,
To fight and break the stronghold down,
  The enemy confound.</stanza>
	<stanza type="verse" number="3">Teach us to pray and use Thy rod
  In strong, prevailing prayer,
Beneath Thy blood to shake the earth
  And powers of the air.</stanza>
	<stanza type="verse" number="4">By prayer and faith, O may we learn
  To labor, Lord, with Thee,
To know the victory is ours
  And Thine authority.</stanza>
  </lyrics>
